- **HH:MM UTC** — event, who did what, what they observed

## Impact
Customers affected, features degraded, SLA/SLO breach, revenue or trust impact.

## Contributing Factors
Root cause(s) and contributing factors. Include technical (code, config, infra) AND systemic (process, monitoring, alerting, runbooks, on-call load, knowledge gaps).

## What Went Well
Detection speed, team response, tooling that helped.

## What Went Poorly
Delays, false starts, missing signals, ambiguous ownership.

## Corrective Actions
Populate `action_items`. Categorize in the description: **[Prevent]** changes to prevent recurrence / **[Detect]** improve detection / **[Mitigate]** faster response next time. Every item needs owner, due date, priority.

